---
title: Portobello Mushroom Wellingtons with Kale-Cranberry Salad
description: This veggie take on a classic holiday wellington is full of robust flavour. Flaky, golden puff pastry surrounds roasted portobello mushrooms on a thyme-scented spinach filling.
